Unknown.name: MobileClient
Unknown.summary: An Easy to use Google Play Music Client, that can do everything but upload music.

constructors.name: MobileClient(string token)
constructors.summary: Create aMobileClientthat has previously been logged in, using the specified Authorization Token.
constructors.remarks: To Check if the Authorization Token is still valid see:

methods.name: GetConfig()
methods.summary: Get the Google Play Music configuration key / values

methods.name: GetListenNowSituations(int[] situationType)
methods.returns: Information like: - "Its Friday Morning..." : "Play Music for..." - "Todays Biggest Hits" - "Today's Dance Smashes" - "Today's Pop Charts" - "..." - "Waking Up Happy" - "Star Guitars" - "Air Guitar Heroes" - "..." - "..." All Data above will also haveArtReference's for each station / situation

params.value: The situation types you wish to receive

methods.name: GetListenNowSituationsAsync(int[] situationType)

params.value: The situation types you wish to receive

methods.name: ListListenNowTracks()
methods.summary: Gets a list of suggestions (Albums or Stations).
methods.returns: Information like: - "Skin" : "Flume" : "Skin is a music album by Flume" - Reason: "New Release because you like this artist" - "Tourist Radio" - Reason: "Similar to Hayden James" Each Entry will have two images, one with an aspect ratio of 1 and another with aspect ratio of 2. Each Entry will contain either a RadioStation or an Album, never both.

methods.name: ListPlaylists(int numberOfResults)
methods.summary: Gets a list ofPlaylist's associated to the account
methods.returns:
A DataSet ofPlaylist's

Future - TODO (Medium): Add Support for NextPageToken

params.value: How many playlists you wish to receive

methods.name: ListPlaylistsAsync(int numberOfResults)

params.value: How many playlists you wish to receive

methods.name: ListPromotedTracks(int numberOfResults)
methods.returns: A DataSet ofPlaylist's Future - TODO (Low): Maybe Thumbs Up List? Future - TODO (Medium): Add Support for NextPageToken

params.value: How many playlists you wish to receive

methods.name: ListPromotedTracksAsync(int numberOfResults)

params.value: How many playlists you wish to receive

methods.name: ListStationCategories()
methods.summary: Gets a list ofStationCategory's. This is the same as "Browse Stations" on the mobile interface

methods.name: Login(string email, string password)
methods.summary: Login to Google Play Music with the specified email and password. This will make two requests to the Google Authorization Server, and collect an Authorization Token to use for all requests.

params.value: The Email / Username of the google account

methods.syntax: public bool Login(string email, string password)
methods.linkedSyntax: public bool Login(string email, string password)

methods.name: LoginCheck(string token)
methods.summary: Check if the specified Authorization Token is still valid, and if it is collect required information to login.

params.value: The Authorization Token, if left null will use the Authorization Token associated to thisMobileClient(If specified in constructor)
